The data used in this project was obtained from the World Bank's International Debt Statistics database, which can be accessed here: https://www.worldbank.org/en/home.
This dataset encompasses a variety of debt-related indicators that provide insights into the financial health and obligations of countries. The data includes information on public and publicly guaranteed debt, as well as private sector debt, allowing for a comprehensive analysis of national debt dynamics.
The dataset is available in multiple formats, including CSV and Excel, and can be downloaded directly from the World Bank website.
